{"tid":93540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣海軍戰力全球第10　網友瘋狂熱議","createTime":"2017-01-24T13:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T15:06:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df011bca32ebabc2a213824621631b30b117e183","tid":93540,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:23:24.000Z","msg":"Top 10 Most Powerful NAVY In The World 2017 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3UY8Vv8WMaI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3UY8Vv8WMaI&d=5rMhux4GCg7QbMmwUwEGI0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=f777b48e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3UY8Vv8WMaI</a> <br />\n<br />\n日前《批踢踢實業坊》有網友轉貼《YouTube》頻道「Felix 10s」的影片「世界海軍前10強」，內容比較了2016年到2017年間，世界10個國家的海軍陣容。其中台灣登上第10名，與世界各強權並列，引起鄉民們瘋狂熱議。而中國海軍無論在士兵、船隻與戰機等等的數量上，都遠勝印度與日本，看來已經坐穩亞洲第一；第一名的美國，陣仗則是遙遙世界各國，讓網友大呼「美國真的一挑十沒問題」！ <br />\n<br />\n網友們對美國的戰力相當驚嘆：「美國一個打全部應該沒有問題」、「美國壓勝」、「美國被低估了，沒把封存的船算進去」、「幾十年內的結果都是美國痛電全球」、「美帝：今年的保護費快交喔」、「美國超扯」、「難怪中國完全不敢跟美國開戰，連中國自己大官的小孩都送去當美國人」；對於台灣的戰力，不少人則表示：「台灣跟中國海軍挑起來，中共都不一定想打」、「臺灣軍力本來就不弱，是位置太差，隔壁都怪物」、「台灣海島國家，旁邊都兇神惡煞，不強不行啊」、「台灣如果沒有中共恐嚇 何需這麼多軍備」、「台灣一個小島國，可以進全球前十，真的很厲害」；也有人認為「這不就是比數字而已嗎」。"},{"pid":"9ec20af798d725330086a33fcbed4de79536ac53","tid":93540,"uid":51649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:24:52.000Z","msg":"無知第一"},{"pid":"56b2e55acebbf408764b1f34ac4863742a2a07d0","tid":93540,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:27:12.000Z","msg":"台仔哪來的自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b75f7c528136cecf3e6dbdcc904bbf3cfaf4d09","tid":93540,"uid":63801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:30:20.000Z","msg":"支那第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 擺到明比數字而已"},{"pid":"0bf072af12dfb5d1386f87b47b925b7a481d1c89","tid":93540,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38932f4d58ff8c5412c1a6c26dbf3db5a4584a4e","tid":93540,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:38:20.000Z","msg":"當勞侵表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cdfd83739058736fb1ec7557e6cb72e16961745","tid":93540,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:45:27.000Z","msg":"美國出千<br />\n<br />\n集世界各地精英發展（二戰德國科學家）等<br />\n<br />\n中國/俄國 單靠自身民族努力"},{"pid":"b573ce1099c50a28bad108ce30d53946ecdc2f3d","tid":93540,"uid":27688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:47:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國出千<br />\n<br />\n集世界各地精英發展（二戰德國科學家）等<br />\n<br />\n中國/俄國 單靠自身民族努力</blockquote><br />\n重竹要財力屈機 養得起"},{"pid":"81efd06c1e3c3e858d305928c9808f191cde8b80","tid":93540,"uid":35683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:25:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>美國出千<br />\n<br />\n集世界各地精英發展（二戰德國科學家）等<br />\n<br />\n中國/俄國 單靠自身民族努力</blockquote><br />\n重竹要財力屈機 養得起</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n銀紙係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">印</span>出黎㗎，留意下美國<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國債</span>"},{"pid":"77c59963e936d60ce1b97c9d2b198dc3edaff4c7","tid":93540,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:40:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"005e3ab5a912cf75155e49186357740e40960a42","tid":93540,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:48:58.000Z","msg":"下？"},{"pid":"71a9faef3551a6087fb3d9dc1d71cda67e71bc46","tid":93540,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"中國都有咩兵力白皮豬<br />\n認為美國有能力同時應付兩場大型戰爭<br />\n一邊打蛾 一邊打蝗都是無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c3d674be4821e501d225571ec53359a1e8889e","tid":93540,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite